Package: pyis-uploader
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python (>=2.7), python-pycurl, python-progressbar
Recommends: python-gtk2
Description: A uploader for the ImageShack service
 PyIS-Uploader is a powerful tool written in python that uses PycURL to send
 image files to ImageShack, a great site for file shares images.
 .
 Features:
  * A text progress bar indicating the upload progress
  * Support for resize
  * Support for tags
  * Support for upload into account (user/password or cookie)
  * Support for send uploaded image url to X CLIPBOARD (Require python-gtk2)
